i### Via NixOS	/	tilde.team	70
i	/	tilde.team	70
iConcerning the tool configuration, being on NixOS, I decided	/	tilde.team	70
ito use the Emacs module provided by the home-manager. To	/	tilde.team	70
iremain consistent with my current configuration, which is	/	tilde.team	70
ihighly modularized, each Emacs package has its own Nix	/	tilde.team	70
imodule.	/	tilde.team	70
